@startuml
|User|
start

:Top of search/filter flow;

if (user provides keyword?) then (yes)
    :Provide keyword;
    |System|
    :Capture keyword;
    :Filter assets by keyword;
elseif (user provides status?) then (yes)
    :Provide status;
    |System|
    :Capture status;
    :Filter assets by status;
else
    |System|
    :Display full asset list;
endif

|System|
:Update asset table;

|User|
:Select / act on filtered assets (view details, reserve, download doc, etc);

if (new input received?) then (yes)
    --> :Top of search/filter flow;
else (no)
    stop
endif
